        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #1e40af; margin-top: 4px;">This month</div>
    </div>
    <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d1fae5, #a7f3d0); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px;">
        <div style="font-size: 13px; color: #065f46; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px;">üí∞ TOTAL DEBITS</div>
        <div style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; color: #065f46;">‚Ç±8.5M</div>
        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #065f46; margin-top: 4px;">This month</div>
    </div>
    <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fee2e2, #fecaca); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px;">
        <div style="font-size: 13px; color: #991b1b; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px;">üí∏ TOTAL CREDITS</div>
